"bdb8364\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1944903 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"1944903\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d0c949f elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d0c949f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Monthly Giving<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-208b964 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"208b964\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Join the heart of our mission as a Shelter Helper through our monthly giving program, a flexible way to support those in need. Transitioning to automatic, monthly contributions not only simplifies the giving process but also ensures a steady stream of support, allowing us to meet the critical needs of those we serve, precisely when they need it most.<\/p><p><b>Discover the remarkable difference your monthly contributions can make:<\/b><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c8232ff elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c8232ff\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul style=\"font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><li style=\"font-size: 17px;\">$35: ensures clean sheets await every new resident, offering comfort and dignity.<\/li><li style=\"font-size: 17px;\">$50: supplies 100 diapers, providing essential care for the littlest ones in our shelters.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\