lter for a family of four, protecting them from the uncertainty of the night.<\/li>\n \t<li style=\"font-size: 17px;\">$200: affords a month of nutritious after-school snacks, fueling young minds for success.<\/li>\n \t<li style=\"font-size: 17px;\">$500: champions a shelter graduate&#8217;s future through college or trade scholarships, paving the way for a brighter future and self-sufficiency.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0626bf2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0626bf2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tFlexibility is key in our program, allowing you to adjust or pause your donations at any time. Your monthly gift is more than a donation; it&#8217;s a lifeline for our clients, ensuring that Carpenter\u2019s Shelter continues to be a place of hope and help. We are grateful for your generosity and commitment to making a difference in the lives of those we serve.\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9b20add e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"9b20add\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-aad2eca e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"aad2eca\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-13ac484 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child\" data-id=\"13ac484\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-266b3f3 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child\" data-id=\"266b3f3\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div cla